  <sect2 role="package">
    <title>Introduction to KWindowSystem</title>

    <para>
      The <application>KWindowSystem</application> package contains a library
      that provides information about the windowing system and allows
      interaction with the windowing system.
    </para>

    &lfs75_checked;

